506
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:18,900
<i> je to v pořádku. </i>

507
00:42:31,370 --> 00:42:35,090
<i> Berete si Yan Mo za svou právoplatnou ženu?</i>

508
00:42:35,090 --> 00:42:38,100
<i>Beru.</i>

509
00:42:38,100 --> 00:42:41,440
